<https://w3id.org/ftr#hasBenchmark> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ftr#Metric> .
<https://w3id.org/ftr#hasBenchmark> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ftr#Benchmark> .
<https://w3id.org/ftr#hasBenchmark> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Property used to link a metric to the benchmarks it belongs to. A metric may belong to many benchmarks."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ftr#hasBenchmark> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has benchmark"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ftr#invokesTest
