<https://w3id.org/ftr#invokesTest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Property used to determine which concrete tests are expected to be invoked by a benchmark scoring algorithm"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ftr#invokesTest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "invokes test"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ftr#outputFromAlgorithm
<https://w3id.org/ftr#outputFromAlgorithm> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
