<https://w3id.org/ftr#outputFromAlgorithm> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ftr#ScoringAlgorithm> .
<https://w3id.org/ftr#outputFromAlgorithm> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relationship to indicate which scoring algorithm was used to obtain a benchmark score from grading a set of test results."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ftr#outputFromAlgorithm> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "output from algorithm"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ftr#outputFromTest
