<https://w3id.org/ftr#outputFromTest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "output from test" .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ftr#scoredTestResults
<https://w3id.org/ftr#scoredTestResults> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ftr#scoredTestResults> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom> .
