<https://w3id.org/ftr#scoredTestResults> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ftr#TestResultSet> .
<https://w3id.org/ftr#scoredTestResults> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relationship designed to link a benchmark score (which contains the value of an assessment) to the set of test results that contain the pass/fail status and are used to create the numeric value of the assessment according to the indications of a scoring algorithm"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ftr#scoredTestResults> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "scored test results"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ftr#scoringFunction
