<https://w3id.org/ftr#scoringFunction> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Property used to link a scoring algorithm with the specification document that indicates how the scoring works. A benchmark may be implemented with one or more scoring algorithms"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ftr#scoringFunction> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "scoring function"@en .
# 
